A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojoji sun harbe 'yan zanga-zangar zaman lafiya da suka kashe mutane 300 yayin da ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai na hagu ke kafa matsayinsu a Latin Amurka.
Lopez Abrador ya nemi gafara ga matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba su kudin makaranta da kuma taimakawa wajen gina jami'o'i.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun ilimi suna janyo hankalin matasa zuwa ga ƙungiyoyin laifi.
Ya kamata a ninka kudaden da Amurka ke bayarwa don amfani da hankali na wucin gadi.
Kamar yadda China ke kara shiga cikin harkar kere kere, Amurka ma ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa a fannin bincike, in ji Kai-Fu Lee, mai bincike da zuba jari a fannin kere kere, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan magana ta fito ne daga sassa daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka, inda aka sanar da cewa Amurka na da kasawar da ta dace a fannin fasaha.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da sabon tsari: tana da burin zama kasa ta farko a fannin kirkirar kere kere ta hanyar kere kere ta hanyar fasaha a shekarar 2030.
Li ya kara da cewa, "Budget din biyu a binciken AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa inda yawancin kasashe ke baya a wannan fannin kuma muna neman mataki na gaba don ci gaba a AI".
Daban-daban kudade na iya ninka yiwuwar Amurka ta sami babbar fasaha ta wucin gadi, in ji Lee a cikin wata hira da aka yi da CNBC a wannan makon.
Li, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa mai suna "All Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" a wannan watan, shine Shugaba na kamfanin Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin fasahar kere kere na kasar Sin.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, Carnegie yayi aiki a Jami'ar Mellon akan tsarin hankali na wucin gadi wanda ya doke mafi girman dan wasan Amurka, kuma a fall ya kasance mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
Lee ya amince da gasa ta fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka ta baya, kamar ta Robotics Challenge na Hukumar Ci Gaban Bincike na Tsaro, don tantance mataki na gaba.
Li ya ce masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati.
"Sinanci ba ya cire shugabannin ilimi; kamfanoni ne ke bayarwa", in ji Li.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da masu ilimin kimiyya daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen da aka yi a manufofin shige da fice na iya taimakawa wajen kara inganta kokarin da Amurka ke yi na kera kere-kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da Green Card ta atomatik ga PhDs a cikin Artificial Intelligence", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa AI na gaba a watan Yuli 2017.
Gidauniyar kimiyyar kimiyyar kasa ta kasar Sin ta bai wa mutane tallafin kudi a fannin ilimi, kamar su National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati, suna kashe kudi ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi a kasar Sin bai da kyau, in ji Li.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa wani cibiyar hadin gwiwa kan ilimin kere kere, wanda ke nufin hada masana'antu da masu ilimi, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamitin zabe kan ilimin kere kere.
Kuma a wannan watan, DRPA ta sanar da zuba jari na dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri mai suna AI Next.
A matsayin NSF, a halin yanzu tana saka sama da dala miliyan 100 a kowace shekara a cikin binciken hankali na wucin gadi.
A halin yanzu, dokar Amurka da ke neman kafa Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa kan Ilimin Artificial Intelligence ba ta sami ci gaba ba cikin watanni.
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar raba gardama kan ko za a canja sunan kasar
A ranar Lahadi ne mutanen Macedonia suka kada kuri'ar raba gardama kan ko za su sauya sunanta zuwa "Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia", wani mataki da zai magance rikicin da ya dade da shekaru da dama da Girka wanda ya hana ta neman shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wacce ke da lardin da ake kira Macedonia, sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa yana wakiltar da'awar yankin ta kuma ta hana shiga NATO da Tarayyar Turai.
Gwamnatocin biyu sun kulla yarjejeniya a watan Yuni kan sabon sunan da aka gabatar, amma masu adawa da kasa sun ce wannan canjin zai lalata asalin asalin Slavic mafiya rinjaye na Macedonia.
Shugaba Georgy Ivanov ya ce ba zai kada kuri'ar ba, kuma yana da shakku kan ko za a iya samun kashi 50 cikin dari na ƙimar da ake buƙata don amincewa da kuri'ar.
Tambayar da aka yi a kuri'ar raba gardama ita ce: "Shin kuna neman zama memba na NATO da Tarayyar Turai tare da amincewa da yarjejeniya da Girka?"
Magoya bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun yi jayayya da biyan kudin shiga cikin Tarayyar Turai da NATO ga Macedonia, daya daga cikin kasashen da suka fito daga rushewar Yugoslavia.
"Na zo ne a yau don in yi zabe a madadin makomar kasar, matasa a Macedonia domin su rayu cikin 'yanci a karkashin inuwar Tarayyar Turai saboda hakan na nufin rayuwa mai aminci ga dukkanmu", in ji Olivera Georgijevska, 79, a Skopje.
Ko da yake ba a tilasta ba, 'yan majalisar sun ce za su bi sakamakon zaben ta hanyar yanke shawara.
Ana bukatar rinjaye biyu bisa uku a majalisar don a canja sunan.
Hukumar zabe ta jihar ta ce babu wani rashin daidaito da aka samu a ranar 1 ga watan Janairu.
Amma, kashi 16 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a sun kada kuri'a, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 34 cikin 100 na zaben majalisar dokoki na 2016, inda kashi 66 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a suka kada kuri'arsu.
"Na zo ne domin in yi zabe saboda 'ya'yana, muna da matsayi a Turai", in ji wani mai jefa kuri'a a Skopje, babban birnin kasar.
Firayim Ministan Macedonia Zoran Zaiev, matarsa Zorica da dansa Dusko sun kada kuri'ar amincewa da sake sunan kasar a zaben raba gardama da za a yi a Strumicat, wanda zai bude hanyar shiga NATO da Tarayyar Turai a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 2018.
Vladimir Kavadarkov, mai shekara 54, yana shirya karamin mataki a gaban majalisar dokokin Skopje, yana kuma ɗaga kujeru a gaban alfarwar da masu ƙin jefa ƙuri'a suka kafa.
"Muna goyon bayan NATO da Tarayyar Turai, amma ba ma son shiga ta kofar sabis, muna son shiga da kawunanmu a sama", in ji Kavadarkov.
"Mu matalauta ne, amma muna da mutunci.
Idan ba sa son su dauki mu a matsayin Macedonia, za mu iya zuwa wasu kamar China da Rasha kuma mu kasance cikin hadin kan Euro-Asia".
PM Zaev ya ce zama memba na NATO zai kawo zuba jari da ake bukata a Macedonia, inda rashin aikin yi ya kai kashi 20.
"Na yi imanin cewa za a sami rinjaye mai yawa saboda sama da kashi 80 cikin 100 na 'yan kasarmu na goyon bayan Tarayyar Turai da NATO", in ji Zaev bayan da ya kada kuri'arsa.
Ya ce sakamakon "Ee" zai zama "tabbatar da makomarmu".
Wani bincike da Cibiyar Nazarin Manufofin Macedonia ta fitar a ranar Litinin ya nuna cewa kashi 30 zuwa 43 cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a za su halarci zaben, wanda ya rage adadin da ake bukata don samun takunkumin.
Wani binciken da Telma TV ta Macedonia ta gudanar ya nuna cewa kashi 57 cikin 100 na masu amsa suna shirin kada kuri'a a ranar Lahadi.
Kashi 70 cikin 100 sun ce za su yi zabe.
Za a samu kashi 50 cikin 100 na kuri'un da za a yi zaben domin a yi nasara.
