LeBron zai buga wa Lakers wasa na farko a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Fans sun kusan gama jiran ganin LeBron James ya fara tafiya a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na wasan da za a yi a ranar Lahadi a San Diego da Denver Nuggets.
Amma har yanzu ba a tantance tsawon lokacin da zai yi wasa ba.
"Zai zama sama da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mike Trudell, mai ba da rahoto ga Lakers, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa na iyakance.
Bayan atisaye a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na shirin wasan Lakers na wasanni shida.
"Ba na bukatar wasan tsinkaye don in shirya kaina a wannan lokaci na aikina", in ji shi.
A lokacin gangamin Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi wani gagarumin gangamin yakin neman zabe a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurrukan da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka dage kuri'ar tabbatar da zabensa na cike wa'adin da ya rage a kotun koli, Trump na kan hanyar samar da goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar asarar iko a kan majalisa bayan an kada kuri'ar a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia ya gudana kuma yaya kake kallon sa a intanet?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na dare, ET, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye ta YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana a wannan makon game da sauraron wanda ya zabi kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya tashi a yayin binciken FBI, tare da kuri'ar tabbatar da majalisar dattijai da ake tsammani, saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i.
Amma, manufar farko ta buɗe waɗannan tarurruka ita ce taimaka wa 'yan Republican su sami ɗan ci gaba a gaban zaɓen Nuwamba.
Kamfanin na Shugaba Trump ya ce, "Manufar tarurruka biyar na mako mai zuwa shine don ƙarfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin kiyayewa da faɗaɗa rinjaye a ƙarƙashin Majalisar Dattijai da Majalisar Wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa, a yayin da muke shiga lokacin kamfen mai cike da aiki, shugaban zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da yawa", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
An shirya taron na yau a Wesenbenko Arena a Wheeling, "yana iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma ɗaukar hoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu tun watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia ya ce, "ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban zai yi kokarin kara karfafa masa gwiwa a zaben ba", a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA ta nuna yunwar gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a gasar zakarun Turai a ranar Lahadi
A ranar Asabar da yamma, bayan an kammala zaman guda uku, an bukaci gasar Ryder Cup.
Dandalin pendulum na Momentum wani sabon ra'ayi ne na wasa amma 'yan wasa sun gaskata da shi, kuma sun fi kowa yin hakan.
To, ina ne Momentum zai ce su je?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka ina ganin muna da ɗan ƙarfi a yanzu", in ji Jordan Speith a yayin da yake tafiya a ranar.
Turai na da fa'ida, tabbas, tana da maki hudu a gaba da sauran wasanni 12.
Kamar yadda Speith ya ce, Amurkawa suna jin cewa suna da wasu taimako a kan hanyarsu kuma suna iya samun ƙarfafa daga abubuwa da yawa, musamman siffar Speith da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma dukansu sun sami maki uku daga hudu.
Speith ya kasance mai kisa daga farko zuwa ƙarshe kuma yana jagorantar daga gaba.
Da yake zagaye na gaba, muryar murna ta ƙara ƙarfi, lokacin da shi da Thomas suka yi wasa mai mahimmanci don ɗaukar wasan ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu, duk da cewa sun faɗi maki biyu.
Wasan da ya ci su a 15 ya samu irin wannan ihu, wanda ya nuna cewa yana ganin cewa Amurka ba ta fi sauran ba.
"Ya kamata ka yi zurfin tunani game da wasan da kake yi", in ji Speeth.
Kowane ɗan wasa yana da shi yanzu.
Rami 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasa da suka fi Speeth da Thomas maki a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francisco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin rashin adalci na gasar Ryder Cup.
Ƙungiyar Turai mai ban mamaki amma mai ban sha'awa ta kasance hudu zuwa hudu kuma ba za ta iya yin kuskure ba.
"Mollywood" ita ce kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi wani fim ba a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma sun yi watsi da fim a ranar Asabar da safe, da yammacin Juma'a da kuma a ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wannan tseren, da kuma yadda suke zuba makamashi daga cikin jama'a, ya nuna cewa sun kasance 'yan wasan da suka yi hasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba wani dan wasan da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari iyawa a matsayin wanda zai iya lashe gasar Turai a lokacin da rana ta sauka a Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau idan suka yi rami biyu a lokaci guda.
Amma, ba a cika magana game da ɗaukaka a Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Web Simpson sun yi wa jarumin kwallon kafa na safe Sergio Garcia wasu matsaloli yayin da suke hulɗa da Alex Naren.
A cikin tara na farko, wani bogie da biyu biyu na Spaniards da Swede sun jefa su cikin rami daga inda ba za su iya tashi ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya fitar da kai daga cikin ramin.
Yana da ban sha'awa sosai a duba Forball da ForSum da kyau saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, da shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, da waɗanda ba su bayarwa, da kuma dabarun da za su iya canzawa nan take.
Turai ta yi wasa mai kyau a matsayin ta kuma ta yi nasara a ranar karshe, amma wannan zaman na Forsam ya kara tabbatar da cewa Team USA na da yunwar fada da wasu, musamman ma da 'yan wasa na jihar suka yi shakku.
Turai ta yi nasara da maki 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai za ta yi amfani da lafiya ta hanyar samun nasara 10-6 a kan Amurka a ranar karshe ta Ryder Cup a wasan Forball da Forsam na ranar Asabar.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francisco Molinari sun ci nasara sau biyu a gasar Golf Nationals, inda suka kai wa Tiger Woods nasara.
Kungiyar Thomas Jorn ta Turai, wacce ke neman dawo da kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara da ci 3-1 a gasar, inda ta kori 'yan wasan Amurka da suka yi rashin nasara a wasannin safe.
Amurka ta lashe wasanni biyu kuma ta ba da shawarar ƙarin juriya a cikin forums, amma ba ta iya cike gibin ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na wasan kwaikwayo a ranar Lahadi don dawo da kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon rookie na Turai da ya sami maki huɗu a jere kuma shi da Molinari, tare, sune kawai biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka sami maki huɗu daga wasanni huɗu na farko bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki.
Woods da Patrick Reed sun yi nasara a wasan kwallon kafa, sannan suka yi nasara sosai a wasan Superblay, inda suka doke Woods da dan wasan Amurka Bryson DeCambiu da kwallaye 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi ta yin fice a wasu lokutan amma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 da ya buga a kwallon kafa da kuma wasan kwallon kafa, kuma a jere bakwai.
Justin Rose, ya yi hutu don wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya koma wurin abokin wasan Forsam, Henrik Stenson, inda ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koppker 2 da 1 - masu lamba daya da uku a duniya.
A wani kyakkyawan rana mai iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris, ko da yake Turai ba ta da kanta.
Manyan masu cin nasara sau uku Jordan Speith da Justin Thomas sun kafa ma'auni ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci nasara mai ƙarfi 2-1 a kan John Rum da Ian Poulter na Spain a wasan kwallon kafa kuma sun dawo da nasara 4-3 a kan Poulter da Rory McIlroy bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko a wasan kwallon kafa.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na biyu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta samu koma baya daga kasa da maki hudu a gasar daya tak, duk da cewa a halin yanzu, tawagar Furyk na bukatar a yi wasa daya ne kawai domin dawo da kofin.
Bayan kasancewa na biyu mafi kyau na kwana biyu, duk da haka, ya yi kama da cewa za a ci gaba da kai hari a ranar Lahadi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makaman ba 'ta hanyar' imani.
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake da shi na kara zurfafa rashin amincewa da Amurka, kuma babu wani damar da kasar za ta iya ba da makaman nukiliya ba tare da son zuciya ba.
Ryong Ho ya fada a taron shekara-shekara na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki matakai masu kyau a bara, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma makaman nukiliya, da kuma karya dakin gwaje-gwajen nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin da ta yi na kada a kara fasahar nukiliya da kuma yaduwar makaman nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan amsa ba a Amurka", in ji shi.
