Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri Rose Leslie, tauraruwar Game of Thrones, tana da shekaru 31, ta yarda cewa tana da matukar damuwa game da matsalar.
'Ni kaina, ina jin sosai, a yanzu - ina ne muke kuskure game da maza?' in ji shi.
