HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100 da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Akwai sama da mutane 820,000 da suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin kamuwa da cutar kusan 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ne saboda yaduwar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da abin da ya faru a baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar jini.
Amma an rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar zuwa kusan sifili, in ji jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin na ƙaruwa zuwa mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An halatta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT.
Saboda dabi'u na gargajiya na kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza suna yin jima'i da maza, kuma suna auren mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin wannan dangantaka.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga jama'a a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
