Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa don "hana" fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Wajen
Washington na iya "yin amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa idan ya cancanta" don hana shigowar man fetur na Rasha zuwa kasashen Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda mai binciken Washington ya bayyana.
