2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Arewacin Sumatra, Indonesia, inda ta haddasa tsunami da ya addabi kasashe 14 da kuma kashe mutane 226,000 a yankin tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
