Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yanke wa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York hukuncin kisa
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York na neman a yanke wa Saifullo Saipow hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da hannu a harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a New York, hukuncin da ba a taba yanke wa kowa ba tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da yin amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar hawan keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba, inda ya yi wa masu hawan keke da masu tafiya da kafa rauni.
Sanarwar da aka shigar a Kotun Kudancin New York ta bukaci a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, ta ce, kafin a zartar da hukuncin kisa, dole ne masu gabatar da kara su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da "sha'awa" kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni.
Dukkanin su biyu sun isa a yanke musu hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardun kotu.
Mako guda bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta gabatar da tuhuma 22 kan Saipov, ciki har da kisa takwas, wanda aka saba da shi a cikin aikata laifuka, da tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Da yake nuna yadda Saipov ya kai harin "mai banƙyama, mai banƙyama da kuma lalata", lauyoyi sun ce "daidai ne a yi shiri da kuma tsinkaya".
Saifullo Habbullayevich Saipow wanda ya yi wa danginsa da abokansa rauni, asarar rai da kuma asarar rai, su ne Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Anne-Laura Decatt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erliz, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Mendoza, sanarwar da aka yi a cikin jihar.
A cikin wadanda suka mutu, biyar daga cikin su 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
An kashe mutum na ƙarshe a gundumar kudu ta New York fiye da shekaru goma da suka shige.
